{"tid":2054280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要預防下一間國際企業奶共，唔該而家開始做野","createTime":"2020-06-07T04:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:37:02.000Z","uid":284147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0ab7049037851820103fd990628920f7d96af4","tid":2054280,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"匯豐正式宣佈係藍店<br />\n<br />\n全世界上twitter 公開佢奶共資訊，呼籲全世界人BOYCOTT 佢<br />\n<br />\n1）永不用佢銀行服務<br />\n2）賣晒佢d股票<br />\n<br />\n記得tag<br />\n#BoycottHSBC @HSBC<br />\n<br />\n點解咁做？ 要預防下一間國際企業出黎奶共！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次如果痛擊到匯豐，下一間國際企業講嘅就會係， 我怕失去全世界70億人口市場， 而吾敢為14億人口市場奶共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pwZ7SO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pwZ7SO.jpg&h=1144aac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d641e6120039c775efab11877e93c4a4acbab768","tid":2054280,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"以後叫上海汇丰银行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2def1886db19409af16e8babdb346daf6a7d4d5","tid":2054280,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"不如喺時事台開過個post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bedbf84f41cb45736eb88c04e67c8195d35397c","tid":2054280,"uid":951